quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  35,45,"Lɑ Wẽnd sã n dɑ yõkdẽ nebã ne b sẽn tʋmã, A kõon n bɑsẽ bõn-yãnemdg tẽngã poor zug ye, lɑ sẽn be bɑlɑ yɑɑ t'A yɑoond-b lɑme n nɑ tãɑg sɑsɑ sẽn yãk tɩ beẽ; tɩ b sɑsɑ wã sã n wɑ tɑ, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ nenem Soɑb ne ɑ yembsã."
  36,1,"Yɑɑ Sɩɩn"
  36,2,"M wẽen ne Alkʋrãanã sẽn bʋ n manegã."
  36,3,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka fo bee tẽn-tʋʋmbã pʋgẽ."
  36,4,"N be so-tɩrg zugu."
  36,5,"N ya wilb Naabã sikri, sẽn yaa yolsg Naabã."
  36,6,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ f bugs neb b sẽn pa bugs b baab-rãmba, tɩ bãmb yaa yam yaal-yaal rãmba."
  36,7,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka gomdã sɩdga b wʋsg fãa zugu, tɩ bãmb pa kõt sɩd ye."
  36,8,"Ad Tõnd ninga b yubliẽ wã goala tɩ b tʋg n teeg b lεmã, tɩ b nensã nake."
  36,9,"La D ning koak b taoorã, la b poorẽ wã me koaka, n lud-b tɩ b pa neẽ ye."
  36,10,"La yaa a ye b zugu, fo bugs-b lame ma fo pa bugs-ba: b pa kõt sɩd ye."
  36,11,"Ad fo sẽn bugsdã yaa ned ning sẽn tũud-a tẽegrã, la a yaeesd Arrahmaan (yolsg) Naabã ne a sẽn lillã fãɑ. Bɩ f noog a sũur ne yaafa la keoor sẽn yaa bedre."
  36,12,"Ad Tõnd n vʋʋgd kũ-rãmbã, la D gʋlsd bũmb ning b sẽn tʋm tɩ reng taoorã, la b vũunã, la bũmbã fãa Tõnd tigim-a-la gaf vẽeneg pʋgẽ."